data.description: Sun-drenched brick charmer nestled on a quiet corner lot - your perfect oasis awaits! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch boasts hardwood floors, living room open to the kitchen, and a bonus room (formerly a garage) brimming with possibilities.Imagine whipping up meals in your bright, new kitchen (choose your own cabinet colors!), then cozying up with family in the inviting living room. Relax around the fire pit, or enjoy weekend getaways to charming Summerville, just a short drive away. This brick ranch, built to last, offers easy access to shopping, restaurants, I-95, and is only 45 Minutes to the Air Base. Don't wait - picture yourself creating memories in this charming home - will consider backup offers
